<headline>Winter Weather Advisory issued January 03 at 2:06PM MST until January 04 at 5:00AM MST by NWS Pocatello</headline>
<description>...WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 5 AM MST
TUESDAY...
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 2 to 5
inches.
* WHERE...Wood River Basin including the cities of Hailey,
Bellevue and Picabo.
* WHEN...From 11 AM Monday to 5 AM MST Tuesday.
* IMPACTS...Plan on difficult driving conditions. Gusty winds
will create low visibility and blowing and drifting snow.</description>
<instruction>Slow down and use caution while traveling.
The latest road conditions can be obtained by calling 5 1 1.</instruction>
